Package net.morbz.minecraft.blocks

Interface Summary
IBlock Interface for all blocks.
 

Class Summary
CustomBlock A custom block for testing purposes and internal functions.
DoorBlock The class for doors of all materials.
Material This class defines all the basic block with their IDs.
PlanksBlock The class for wooden planks.
QuartzBlock The class for a quartz block.
RailBlock The class for basic rails.
RedstoneTorchBlock A redstone torch for both states active and inactive.
SpecialRailBlock The class for special rails (powered, detector and activator).
StainedBlock A class for all blocks that have a stained version (glass, wool, carpet, clay).
StainedBlock.StainedMaterial The material of the stained block.
 

Enum Summary
DirtBlock The class for the dirt and podzol blocks.
DoorBlock.DoorMaterial The material of which the door consists.
DoorBlock.HingeSide The site on which the hinge is.
QuartzBlock.QuartzFacing The facing of the quartz block.
QuartzBlock.QuartzVariant The variant of the quartz block.
RailBlock.RailCurve  
SandBlock The class for sand and red sand.
SandstoneBlock The class for sandstone blocks with different structures.
SimpleBlock The class for all blocks that don't have block data.
SpecialRailBlock.SpecialRailMaterial The type of the special rail.
StainedBlock.StainedColor The color of the stained block.
StoneBlock The class for the stone, granite, etc.
StoneBrickBlock The stone brick block with different structures.
